name: Susanoo
description:
Susanoo, is the brother of Amaterasu. he was born from Izanagi's nose when he was purified after returning from hell.
Susanoo is one of the three gods who are the "Three Precious Children" along with Amaterasu (goddess of the sun) and Tsukuyomi (god of moon). Susanoo is known for his destructive and deceptive nature. Susanoo is also famous for having fought the eight headed dragon "Yamata no Orochi" and defeated it.
